Subject: Tom Bowman,Aridzona

Tom Bowman was a long time builder of VW motors and trannys.  For many years
he never missed a VW swap meet with his super clean VW parts.  A true
Gentleman and a dedicated VW man.

 

Tom passed away about a week ago.  

 

Memorial services well be held at Church of Jesus Christ of Latter day
Saints, 3010 East Thunderbird in Phoenix. February 25th,  11: AM.

 

If you can attend,  Please wear a Volkswagen shirt. 
